Pergunta 1)

a) 1^2 + 2^2 + 3^2 + 4^2 = 1 + 4 + 9 + 16 = 30
b) (3*1) + (3*2) + (3*3) + (3*4) = 3 + 6 + 9 + 12 = 30
c) (3-2*1) + (3-2*2) + (3-2*3) + (3-2*4) = 1 + (-1) + (-3) + (-5) = -8
d) (2*1 + X) + (2*2 + X) + (2*3 + X) = (2+X) + (4+X) + (6+X) 
e) 0(0-1)(5-0) + 1(1-1)(5-1) + 2(2-1)(5-2) + 3(3-1)(5-3) + 4(4-1)(5-4) + 5(5-1)(5-5) = 0 + 0 + 6 + 12 + 12 + 0 = 30
f) (8k - 6*1) + (8k - 6*2) + (8k - 6*3) + (8k - 6*4) = (8k -6) + (8k -12) + (8k -18) + (8k -24)
